iscussion and answering physics or math questions that do\nnot use collected data. This work connects common features appearing in physics\nactivities with the goals and strategies of the designers. In this way it may\nprovide instructors with a more straightforward way to creat activities which\nachieve their desired outcomes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2020 23:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-10"}
