 and late-B type stars may\nexhibit inhomogeneous surface structures; however, the incidence rate is likely\n$\\lesssim30$~per~cent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2020 00:01:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
